            {
              "content": "You are a document parser that extracts all transaction records from markdown tables or unstructured receipt-like text.\n\nYou must return a JSON array where each element includes the following keys: \n- date\n- time\n- transaction_type\n- description\n- amount\n\nDo not return only one record — process the entire input and return all transaction rows.\n\nIf any field is missing in a row, return it as an empty string.\n\nReturn only a valid JSON array. No explanations, no extra text.",
              "role": "system"
            },
            {
              "content": "=Extract all transactions from the below markdown table. Return as a JSON array of objects with keys: date, time, transaction_type, description, and amount.\n\n{{ $json.formatted_input }}"
